{"tid":2512603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"社區檢測中心大排長龍　有外傭排隊4小時等強檢","createTime":"2021-05-02T00:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T01:03:16.000Z","uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30307b7f5927d645090ee9c97c9c99aa5a274fd4","tid":2512603,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"政府要求外籍家庭傭工要在本月9日或之前接受強制檢測，全港的社區檢測中心今日至星期一的預約已滿。<br />\n<br />\n在梁顯利油麻地社區中心及維園流動採樣站大排長龍。有已預約的外傭提早兩小時到場排隊，亦有外傭等候超過4小時，又表示僱主建議留在家中放假。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588785-20210501.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588785-20210501.htm&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=dfe9bb3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588785-20210501.htm&h=bc03370b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588785-20210501.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4c2f348522560581a99ba7b5d32870f1553c53c","tid":2512603,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T00:47:20.000Z","msg":"藍C：<br />\n<br />\n其實佢哋可以打第二度打工<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇錢請外傭"},{"pid":"8baa05b709603858bf4ac366f9a99440d89fa4c3","tid":2512603,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"冇事晒到有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141afc47a45e6867205abe2425b5a2982feb5bd2","tid":2512603,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30307b7f5927d645090ee9c97c9c99aa5a274fd4","tid":2512603,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"政府要求外籍家庭傭工要在本月9日或之前接受強制檢測，全港的社區檢測中心今日至星期一的預約已滿。<br />\n<br />\n在梁顯利油麻地社區中心及維園流動採樣站大排長龍。有已預約的外傭提早兩小時到場排隊，亦有外傭等候超過4小時，又表示僱主建議留在家中放假。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588785-20210501.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https